OL,3,C'He was neglected': Adults with
OL,4,Clearning disabilities dying 20 years
OL,5,Cearly
OL,7,FITV News has highlighted the scandal,
OL,8,Fhearing from people with learning
OL,9,Fdisabilities and their families who
OL,10,Fsay their health concerns were
OL,11,Fdismissed or not taken seriously by
OL,12,Fauthorities, as ITV News
OL,13,FInvestigations Editor Daniel Hewitt
OL,14,Freports
OL,16,FPeople with learning disabilities in
OL,17,FEngland are dying 20 years younger
OL,18,Fthan the general population, a new NHS
OL,19,Freport has revealed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
