OL,3,C'He was neglected': Adults with
OL,4,Clearning disabilities dying 20 years
OL,5,Cearly
OL,7,FAlmost 40% of deaths of learning
OL,8,Fdisabled people were found to be
OL,9,Favoidable, almost double the rest of
OL,10,Fthe population.
OL,12,FCampaigners have described the
OL,13,Ffindings as shocking and unacceptable.
OL,15,FThe latest 'Learning from Lives and
OL,16,FDeaths report (LeDeR)', an annual
OL,17,Fstudy into the deaths of learning
OL,18,Fdisabled and autistic people
OL,19,Fcommissioned by NHS England, looked at
OL,20,F3,556 deaths in 2023.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
