OL,5,Cearly
OL,7,FIt found the average age of death was
OL,8,F62.5, a slight improvement on the year
OL,9,Fbefore, when it was 62.2.
OL,11,FEthnic minorities with a learning
OL,12,Fdisability die even younger, at 56.9
OL,13,Fyears of age, for Asian people, the
OL,14,Faverage age of death was 43.2.
OL,16,FThat is incredibly young compared to
OL,17,Fthe general population, who live on
OL,18,Faverage to 82.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
