OL,7,FLeDeR found the most common causes of
OL,8,Favoidable deaths were flu and
OL,9,Fpneumonia (14.9%), followed by cancers
OL,10,Fof the digestive organs (9.7%) and
OL,11,Fcoronary heart disease (9.5%).
OL,13,FJon Sparkes, Mencap's CEO, told ITV
OL,14,FNews that there are a number of
OL,15,Freasons for health inequalities for
OL,16,Fpeople with learning disabilities and
OL,17,Fautism.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
