OL,3,C'He was neglected': Adults with
OL,4,Clearning disabilities dying 20 years
OL,5,Cearly
OL,7,F"Late diagnosis is one of them. Lower
OL,8,Frates of screening is another. Health
OL,9,Fsystems being inaccessible, or not
OL,10,Fcommunicating effectively with people
OL,11,Fwith learning disabilities.
OL,13,F"It really is not acceptable when we
OL,14,Fare dealing with something as
OL,15,Fimportant as people dying early and
OL,16,Ftwice as many are considered to be
OL,17,Favoidable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
