OL,7,FIn May 2023, he had a fall at his care
OL,8,Fhome and was admitted to hospital, but
OL,9,Fit wasn't the fall that killed Eddie,
OL,10,Fbut a lack of care in hospital.
OL,12,FEddie died in June 2023 from
OL,13,Faspiration pneumonia, an infection
OL,14,Fcaused by fluid or matter passing into
OL,15,Fthe lungs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
