OL,3,C'He was neglected': Adults with
OL,4,Clearning disabilities dying 20 years
OL,5,Cearly
OL,7,FThis was caused by nurses feeding
OL,8,FEddie jelly, despite it being
OL,9,Frepeatedly highlighted as a food not
OL,10,Fto be given as it carried a high risk
OL,11,Fof aspiration due to Eddie's
OL,12,Fdysphagia, a choking condition.
OL,14,FTeresa and Mary, Eddie's sisters, told
OL,15,FITV News how their brother was
OL,16,Fneglected due to his learning
OL,17,Fdisability and was powerless to do
OL,18,Fanything.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
