OL,3,C'He was neglected': Adults with
OL,4,Clearning disabilities dying 20 years
OL,5,Cearly
OL,7,F"It was a lack of understanding of his
OL,8,Fcondition. People didn't take the time
OL,9,Fto learn about him and understand what
OL,10,Fhis needs were, to keep him safe.
OL,12,F"Eddie was a lost voice."
OL,14,FIn July 2025, a coroner ruled that
OL,15,FEddie died through neglect - his death
OL,16,Fwas wholly avoidable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
