OL,7,FRahima Begum, 28, has a learning
OL,8,Fdisability and cerebral palsy. She is
OL,9,Fcared for at home by her mum in East
OL,10,FLondon. She told ITV News she is
OL,11,Ffearful every time she needs medical
OL,12,Ftreatment.
OL,14,FWhen she had to go to the hospital for
OL,15,Fa chest infection, she said: "I was
OL,16,Fconstantly fighting for respect.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
