OL,5,Cearly
OL,7,FThe latest report was due to be
OL,8,Fpublished in 2024, but was delayed due
OL,9,Fto what the Department of Health
OL,10,Fcalled "data issues".
OL,12,FITV News has heard from sources close
OL,13,Fto the programme that staff face
OL,14,Fpotential redundancies, and the
OL,15,Fupcoming abolition of NHS England is
OL,16,Fcausing concerns about the report's
OL,17,Ffuture.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
