OL,7,FAn NHS spokesperson said: "While this
OL,8,Freport shows encouraging progress, it
OL,9,Fis clear there is much more to do to
OL,10,Fmeet the needs of people with a
OL,11,Flearning disability and autistic
OL,12,Fpeople.
OL,14,F"The NHS has rolled out training to
OL,15,Fmore than three million health and
OL,16,Fcare staff to improve the care offered
OL,17,Fto Learning Disability and Autism
OL,18,Fpatients, and all disabled people have
OL,19,Fa 'reasonable adjustment digital flag'
OL,20,Fso they are recognised and care for
OL,21,Fappropriately when getting NHS support.
